1. *Bojao* sam se da će mi ispuniti želju. (I was afraid he would fulfill my wish.)
2. On se *bojao* da će zakasniti na sastanak. (He was afraid he would be late for the meeting.)
3. Mi smo se *bojali* da će biti loše vreme. (We were afraid it would be bad weather.)
4. *Bojimo se* zmija. (We are afraid of snakes.)
5. Ti si se *bojao* da nećeš položiti ispit. (You were afraid you wouldn't pass the exam.)
6. Oni su *bojali* odeću u svim bojama. (They dyed clothes in all colors.)
7. Ja se *bojim* visine. (I am afraid of heights.)
8. *Bojila* sam kosu pre dve nedelje. (I dyed my hair two weeks ago.)
9. On *boji* jaja za Uskrs. (He colors eggs for Easter.)
10. Nisam se *bojao* da će se nešto loše dogoditi. (I wasn't afraid that something bad would happen.)